data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Fishes of Sikhote-Alin State Nature Biosphere Reserve Named After K. G. Abramov

Fishes Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in Sikhote-Alin State Nature Biosphere Reserve Named After K. G. Abramov (Russian Federation) consisting of 710 records collected during 64 years between 1946 and 2015.
